  <description><![CDATA[<p>The well-run and welcoming Hotel Beausite has comfortable and modern furnishings throughout and sits in charming gardens where you can marvel picturesque views. <a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a> centre and transport links is a short walk away, or take the free bus which stops just 200 metres from the hotel. </p>
<p>Under the management of the lovely Max and Imi Ritter, this delightful, family-run hotel retains a quintessential Swiss charm and quality of service. The hotel has charming gardens to the rear where you can relax on sun loungers. Other facilities include an attractive lounge and rustic bar - the perfect spot to enjoy a drink.</p>
<p>Bedrooms are spacious and face the mountains or gardens.</p>
<p><span>Transfer Approx. 2hrs 30 mins by rail from Zurich airport or</span> 3hrs by rail from Geneva airport. <span>Your journey involves 1 or 2 changes of train.</span></p>]]></description>
